channel.title: Need Compiler Help
channel.description:
So I worked on my compilers for a while . I am new to java and looking for answers if you have questions or need me to find something please give it in simple terms in a way even a new person would know. :)
Anyways, my Client compilers is giving me the 100 errors' at first I thought it was nothing after a while of research I've seen a lot of people saying it is cause by the brackets in the codes and java just cannot read it properly.
[img]http://img842.imageshack.us/img842/9282/32z5.png[/img]
You see I'm not exactly sure if I went to the correct spot but I found this ?
[img]http://i.imgur.com/agZzhPL.png[/img]
As for my Source's Compiler this error comes up. [img]http://img802.imageshack.us/img802/8969/pnh9.png[/img]
This one I'm almost clue less as to how to fix it.
I cannot pay someone to help me I'm really sorry . But if I can get some answers to help me so I can make my first rsps , which so far is looking pretty good "been working on it with a friend." I would be very appreciative. Feel free to give harsh comments but please be willing to help if you do. I want to learn and I'm ready.
